name the project
.....
install tailwind, redux and others,
install react-router-dom
design file structure
src/
├── components/           👉 Navbar, Footer ইত্যাদি
├── layouts/              👉 MainLayout (যেখানে navbar + footer থাকবে)
├── pages/                👉 সব পেজ ফাইল
├── routes/               👉 AppRouter.tsx (রাউট কনফিগারেশন)
├── redux/                👉 Redux Store এবং Slice গুলো
└── App.tsx   

set Mainlayout.tsx file

then set router.tsx or appRouters.
then render main.tsx 
then set a error page component and set it approuter errorElement
 


